{"tid":718983,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"隻貓打針後吽就成個半星期","createTime":"2018-06-27T06:03:51.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-27T07:00:56.000Z","uid":36357,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"004b4ee84e4ff18651f1b134cbab2644c247a0d0","tid":718983,"uid":36357,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-27T06:03:51.000Z","msg":"上上星期日帶咗我隻四個月大嘅貓打防疫針(第一針)，打完之後佢吽到今日唔係好想郁，開頭幾日食少咗嘢唔點郁，呢幾日直頭唔食乾糧，迫佢食啲濕糧罐淨係食少少，水又飲少咗好多，屎屎就有食嘢先有，，即係呢幾日無。。。尿都叫有，其他方面都無話唔正常，請問其實係咪佢病咗，定支針藥力未散，好擔心。。。"},{"pid":"b690b8a9844637e37664214f505d93c7986aaf28","tid":718983,"uid":65847,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-27T06:09:08.000Z","msg":"如果唔係打咗濛仔針就睇多次醫生啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beg_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1a7703dc27f1b7d029a1b5eb187a7bdf931ec0a","tid":718983,"uid":73043,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-27T06:19:16.000Z","msg":"無可能wo"},{"pid":"736b340a023554f31355a6fef32fa75cf8e71ca8","tid":718983,"uid":36357,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-27T07:00:56.000Z","msg":"而家book左聽日再睇醫生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n今晚試下用無頭針筒打啲水同濕糧畀佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}